{"code":0,"msg":"ok","data":{"article":{"authorCode":"admin","authorName":"孙天骁","classify":"观点类","content":"<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/article%2F1488279760.png\" title=\"article/1488279760.png\" alt=\"blob.png\" style=\"float: right;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">看完发布会，我觉得这是一款出色的手机。小米5c拥有惊艳的颜值、惊艳的相机，以及配备了快充和type-c接口，我觉得这是一款可以跟oppo r9s竞争的产品。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有几个槽点很想说一下。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. 不支持全网通。只支持移动的4G和联通的2G。我觉得这是这款手机的最大缺点。但是由于搭载的是小米第一款自主研发的处理器，在通讯基带方面的积累不够，这也是有情可原的。雷军说这款芯片的基带是支持软件升级的，期待未来能够带来更多的网络支持。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. 2860mAh的电池。这块电池比小米5的电池容量还要小，但我印象中oppo r9的电池容量也大概是这个数值，总比魅族PRO6的2500多毫安时的电池带X25要好得多。雷军说澎湃S1芯片是很省电的，而且这部手机是小米自己的芯片、系统、手机配合，想必优化也会比正常情况好上一个层次。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3. 3GB的内存。看到很多人吐槽说为什么不上4GB甚至跟360一样的6GB。我觉得这个完全没有必要，运行内存容量再怎么大也都是LPDDR3规格的。跟小米4C相比，小米4c的3+32GB发布时售价1499元，而5C同样价钱是3+64GB的版本，已经存在了不小的进步。对于大部分非手机发烧友的朋友尤其是女性来说，她们是把存储容量看得比运行内存重的。这也和这款手机比较女性化的外观相配。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">其他想说的，比如芯片的28nm工艺，比骁龙625要落后不少。这个作为小米的第一款芯片也是没有办法的事情。我相信假如雷军说芯片的优化很好，那么它就绝对差不到哪里去而且配得上这个价位。这款手机搭载了和米5一样的前置指纹识别，这点肯定不会有人喷。但是网络上的很多人总是忽略它的优点而对它的缺点抓着不放。没有支持全网通确实遗憾，我本人也在用电信卡。但是身边总是还有很多人只用移动的卡，推荐他们买一台5c也是个不错的选择，不要被蓝绿大厂坑了。</p><p><br style=\"color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.8em; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;Noto Sans CJK SC&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 27px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">注：以上纯理论分析。我也很期待尽快看到详细的评测视频来判断搭载首款松果芯片的小米5c的优化到底怎么样，以及还有没有其他的硬伤。</p>","createTime":"2017-02-28 19:03:19","customCoverKey":"","id":181,"isGood":false,"isTop":false,"publicState":0,"replyCount":0,"state":0,"tags":["小米","小米公司","小米手机","松果芯片","澎湃S1"],"title":"如何评价小米5c？","urlCode":"3ZBGCUHSFS","viewCount":772,"viewGroup":-1,"authPassed":true},"author":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}}}